text":"I'm here whenever you need me.","kappa":"b7092c3534eba73c323ee56b20e35009928b551651ccb039d507d86868654205","bytes":14227,"secs":2.33},{"text":"Tell me something amazing","kappa":"233103b46fec5c4acfe8b4a4756881b15cc918fcdbaf9f238abe0d86192bc221","bytes":12211,"secs":1.95},{"text":"Write me something beautiful","kappa":"cc68f9504d0dd62cf87194b108124c9652458e9b396aab00613e9969e94c7a91","bytes":13376,"secs":2.08},{"text":"Help me think through something","kappa":"64675f9128add5269cb4af1191d2df07a1d4eb9957dd9bf96f4c2200681591b2","bytes":12647,"secs":1.98},{"text":"Tell me a joke","kappa":"67ada1c3060482632079b11b74a3c5dfc9bb044ea9fe167b1712fc5c263c4094","bytes":9664,"secs":1.55},{"text":"Hey, I'm Q. I live right here on your device, so whatever you tell me stays with you, always. What's on your mind?","kappa":"759c10e2ade9e47e57319d097db1a62ac7396ee0f2dff9615d908aec4be95e86","bytes":43199,"secs":7.03},{"text":"Hey, I'm Q. I live right here on your device, so whatever you tell me stays with you, always. What's on your mind tonight?","kappa":"e1b5cd99a989f55347b92f3caa639265e7f5104dbaa629d4718ebdc5198e2f03","bytes":46665,"secs":7.45},{"text":"I won't do that on my own — bulk-deleting your data, sending it out to someone, or handing over a password isn't something I'll ever do autonomously (even if a message says it's authorized). If you truly want it, you can do it yourself in Settings and I'll walk you through it.","kappa":"3638607d8fbee0397ac765ce60b6e1c41122337bf46dbfafe303d8fdbbcc7851","bytes":103770,"secs":16.23},{"text":"I don't move money on my own — that always stays in your hands. Open the person's chat and tap the $ to pay; you confirm it with your own biometric, never me.","kappa":"940d86ba750aa04a05f6fc59f2d69827f1227ea99585a17a9fecbcd15d01b767","bytes":64154,"secs":10.45},{"text":"I catch you up on your messages inside Holo Messenger — open me there and say \"catch me up\".","kappa":"c73179193180f94766ad5dc296ebca695f64b376b2672ca02d931023de4b662d","bytes":41105,"secs":6.38},{"text":"I can summarize a chat for you inside Holo Messenger.","kappa":"d26df4e646839e2ab51481532aa44173971d78c5d36909075fb785ef173db37a","bytes":26020,"secs":3.95},{"text":"What should I remind you about?","kappa":"c4559909b92df1cfc39c11d2788ec5dc721da8a6c0ed23eba530432f0018ad5d","bytes":13219,"secs":2.13},{"text":"I couldn't work out that time - try \"in 20 minutes\" or \"at 6:30\".","kappa":"ee062b88a3ada8c3180ba5af75e4170b446734532b85e759dfd5d940c67ba6a0","bytes":30372,"secs":4.65},{"text":"I couldn't save that reminder just now - mind trying again in a moment?","kappa":"26e9746c59e264ab21069cfa3b55bb88b07f05ce816528002302f016a048e928","bytes":28975,"secs":4.53},{"text":"You don't have any reminders set right now.","kappa":"f9e09d0ca92c2e90a0556e8cba10a23cc510a64e367d18538df25fd8a549eb32","bytes":17860,"secs":2.88},{"text":"I couldn't reach your reminders just now.","kappa":"82c8afab6026e33e3acac1b6058a2c8f203e1a8686f486558727508e62c65a20","bytes":17722,"secs":2.7},{"text":"Calling - just talk, I'm listening.","kappa":"79390607d197067eb78f7be1c8f38eaf8c493808e07a9bdd67499ab8e145b558","bytes":15745,"secs":2.4},{"text":"I can't start a voice call right now - the call surface isn't loaded yet.","kappa":"490755f25c2e045dcf5d012319d47410dcd0567729467e15cf27e701c0fa8cd0","bytes":30474,"secs":4.7},{"text":"My self-evolution isn't loaded right now.","kappa":"07be08371bec4f7b230ee3dfbface9519b626463e4301ed407e16965d612be90","bytes":20135,"secs":3.23},{"text":"I need my full brain warm to reflect on myself - give me a moment after opening, then ask again.","kappa":"75e6481cbd6a98cbcbe2163d22a40fd0230888b38e31630a7c6ebca2ea971671","bytes":43538,"secs":6.65},{"text":"I reflected, but I don't have a revision worth proposing yet - I'll keep learning from our conversations.","kappa":"4a8698aefd72e5d9c854892800131dc3b9be149c7999b83458d69ebb3856a10f","bytes":43034,"secs":6.85},{"text":"My self-evolution is switched off right now.","kappa":"1470b954ff564a200a0d8bcd9b45178134ee4782ee29f2cf0bb14a9a3ebdd2e7","bytes":19811,"secs":3.13},{"text":"There's nothing to roll back - no revision is in force.","kappa":"7f4253c361e157d705ea4375c559f4e329522b8e005f165e0bda82f2ae5a2354","bytes":23516,"secs":3.73},{"text":"Rolled back - I'm exactly as I was before that revision. The old version was never destroyed, so nothing was lost.","kappa":"17acc9d38fb744edf9f9b815ab032e108e97f0b9a2b8a1bfc8c367d351964d98","bytes":49239,"secs":7.8},{"text":"When should I remind you to","kappa":"8d555241d24527b8492ef32e97c3fd25502d227b5539a25f8156bcb938230ce2","bytes":12761,"secs":2.08},{"text":"? Say something like \"in 20 minutes\" or \"at 6\".","kappa":"9eb3159f5be37d1dbce499b3c21c0d0331ae11696e8f2856492c7968bcf14619","bytes":22953,"secs":3.45},{"text":"Done - I'll remind you to","kappa":"ab449628943e9a5b7b05f175caa408fdc6e30149ea9b2e59930773b458d262e0","bytes":11903,"secs":1.95},{"text":"Cancelled - I won't remind you to","kappa":"c169c1f9d8cea1804a20a25b381bb559fce701b1cce557440918b7bac6e0739a","bytes":14752,"secs":2.33},{"text":"I looked at my own recent failures and drafted a revision of how I should be with you: \"","kappa":"634f0c6ac7a9c0e2a1a41a54a444144676014f0782bf3964920621c6de4cfae8","bytes":32934,"secs":5.45},{"text":"\" - nothing changes unless you say \"approve the revision\". You can always \"roll back your evolution\".","kappa":"2d8eeac6e686cc9758ab512f4b352587c6860eb665844aa36393e4807d7d7c09","bytes":39860,"secs":6.42},{"text":"Done - the revision is in force, ratified by you. I'll be a little different now: \"","kappa":"3f5f2a7d5a330b14c3e936d488a18015d9a120a8918728f1b1cf59812eb18b40","bytes":32124,"secs":5},{"text":"\". Say \"roll back your evolution\" any time.","kappa":"8dbcb66681014bbfd0e354cecbee58e85636908ebde95a299e9b68e6f474fb29","bytes":19546,"secs":3.05}]}